&lt;p data-start=&quot;477&quot; data-end=&quot;794&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;477&quot; data-end=&quot;490&quot;&gt;PDQ Doors&lt;/strong&gt;—a proud member of the Guild Garage Group—is looking for personable, mechanically inclined, and motivated &lt;strong data-start=&quot;596&quot; data-end=&quot;636&quot;&gt;Garage Door Technicians &amp;amp; Installers&lt;/strong&gt; to join our growing team in Milford, OH. Whether you&#39;re experienced or just getting started, we provide the training, tools, and support to help you succeed.&lt;/p&gt;
