&lt;h1 data-start=&quot;205&quot; data-end=&quot;265&quot;&gt;🚪 Garage Door Sales/Technician&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;266&quot; data-end=&quot;430&quot;&gt;📍 Milford, OH | PDQ Doors | Ohio’s Largest Garage Door Company&lt;br data-start=&quot;329&quot; data-end=&quot;332&quot;&gt;💰 &lt;strong data-start=&quot;335&quot; data-end=&quot;428&quot;&gt;Pay Range: $110,000–$150,000+ annually (uncapped commissions, bonus opportunities)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;432&quot; data-end=&quot;664&quot;&gt;Are you hands-on, mechanically inclined, and motivated by face-to-face customer interactions? Do you enjoy solving problems, working with tools, and earning great pay by helping customers choose the right solutions for their home?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;666&quot; data-end=&quot;998&quot;&gt;At &lt;strong data-start=&quot;669&quot; data-end=&quot;682&quot;&gt;PDQ Doors&lt;/strong&gt;, we’re looking for a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;704&quot; data-end=&quot;761&quot;&gt;Garage Door Technician – Sales &amp;amp; Service Professional&lt;/strong&gt; to join our growing team. This unique role blends &lt;strong data-start=&quot;812&quot; data-end=&quot;868&quot;&gt;in-home consultative sales with &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;812&quot; data-end=&quot;868&quot;&gt;mechanical expertise&lt;/strong&gt;. You won’t just diagnose and fix problems — you’ll also educate homeowners, recommend upgrades, and close the sale on the spot.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;906&quot; data-end=&quot;926&quot;&gt;🔧 Role Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
