&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1143&quot; data-end=&quot;2014&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1143&quot; data-end=&quot;1280&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1145&quot; data-end=&quot;1280&quot;&gt;Diagnose and fix technical issues on residential &amp;amp; commercial garage doors (springs, cables, openers, panels, commercial doors, etc.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1281&quot; data-end=&quot;1407&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1283&quot; data-end=&quot;1407&quot;&gt;Handle installations, maintenance (we use detailed inspections like 24‐point safety checks) and repairs to high standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1408&quot; data-end=&quot;1581&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1410&quot; data-end=&quot;1581&quot;&gt;Engage with customers: understand their needs, explain solutions, offer options, and help them pick the best door/opening system or component for their home or business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1582&quot; data-end=&quot;1671&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1584&quot; data-end=&quot;1671&quot;&gt;Upsell and recommend premium or additional services/products when it adds real value.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
